data.description:
Price Reduced $25,000. Make this your home with the security of a home generator. The  roof and hot water heater had been replaced with in the past few years. The home offers a front setting room and a 3 season room. 2 nice size bedrooms 2 full baths.  Open Living dining area and upgraded kitchen cabinets. Make a few changes and you will have a great home with a lush rear yard.  Community  Center with pool and rec facilities. Lake a few homes away. 
Enjoy and active lifestyle!  
The home is AS IS and buyer responsible for the town CO/CCO/ TOT.
Highest and Best 2/20/24 4pm.
